name: Three Little Birds (unique in this palette)
description: From the collection Three Little Birds: A small series of three little birds in different colors. Each piece shows a different social order between the birds. The birds show their differences and their similarities. Even the position of the bird determines the social relations. The backside of the bird says something to the "family" the bird is loyal to and the front says something to whom the bird is attracted. Have fun understanding the complex relationships of these little birds.
